introduced.

17:59.270 --> 18:01.438
I'm dustin goolsby,
coach of vocal adrenaline.

18:01.505 --> 18:03.206
Oh.

18:03.274 --> 18:04.975
So you're the big
competition at nationals.

18:05.042 --> 18:07.444
Well, thank you very much
for volunteering your star

18:07.511 --> 18:09.946
For our night
of neglect benefit.

18:10.014 --> 18:12.649
What are you talking about?
I never approved that.

18:12.717 --> 18:16.486
Let me cut to
the sexy chase.

18:16.554 --> 18:18.054
