many more years

18:18.122 --> 18:19.522
You have left of
productive ovulating.

18:19.590 --> 18:22.359
Those aren't eggs in
those fallopian tubes.

18:22.426 --> 18:24.394
They're rare,
exotic pearls.

18:24.462 --> 18:26.963
Oh. So you're trying
to seduce me.

18:27.031 --> 18:28.999
Jackpot. This hairline
is 85% my own,

18:29.066 --> 18:31.034
And my sperm count
is off the charts.

18:31.102 --> 18:32.636
Well... (laughs)

18:32.703 --> 18:35.972
...As tempting as that sounds,
I have a boyfriend.

18:36.040 --> 18:37.274
Yeah, you do now.

18:37.341 --> 18:39.476
Admit it.
I'm handsome,

18:39.543 --> 18:41.478
I'm good-looking, and
I'm easy on the eyes.

18:41.545 --> 18:43.313
Also, I'm gorgeous.

18:43.381 --> 18:46.916
And I'm dating
will schuester.

18:46.984 --> 18:48.251
Let me tell you something
about will schuester.

18:48.319 --> 18:49.986
That guy has
tiny baby hands.

18:50.054 --> 18:52.022
Seriously. It's weird.

18:52.089 --> 18:55.091
Once I saw him try to pick up a
big mac, and he couldn't do it.

18:55.159 --> 18:56.526
He had to eat it
layer by layer.

18:56.594 --> 18:58.895
Teeny, tiny, wee

18:58.963 --> 19:00.163
Baby hands.

19:00.231 --> 19:03.199
That are big enough
to knock your teeth out.

19:03.267 --> 19:04.801
Well, this is awkward.

19:06.537 --> 19:08.571
Consider my offer.

19:10.775 --> 19:11.975
What offer?

19:12.043 --> 19:13.310
He was just
hitting on me.

19:13.377 --> 19:15.211
Isn't that silly?

19:17.615 --> 19:19.115
What's wrong?

19:19.183 --> 19:21.418
Well, we were supposed to have
lunch, and you don't show.

19:21.485 --> 19:23.853
And now you're getting hit on
by the coach of our archrival.

19:23.921 --> 19:25.655
How is that my fault?

19:25.723 --> 19:27.624
And by the way, I did
show up for lunch,

19:27.692 --> 19:29.092
And you looked like
you were actually having

19:29.160 --> 19:31.194
A pretty good time.

19:31.262 --> 19:34.164
I kind of felt
like I was intruding, so...

19:34.231 --> 19:35.632
Oh, man. I am...

19:35.700 --> 19:37.434
I am not the jealous type, will.

19:37.501 --> 19:39.336
Neither am I.

19:39.403 --> 19:43.373
Look, how about instead
of a pointless argument,

19:43.441 --> 19:45.775
We rehearse our duet
for the benefit?

19:45.843 --> 19:49.679
I really don't, uh, feel in the
mood to do a duet right now.

19:51.248 --> 19:53.550
I think I just have
to clear my head.

19:56.253 --> 19:59.055
Uh, no problem.

20:02.026 --> 20:04.394
I'll see you at the benefit.

20:06.397 --> 20:09.532
(school bell ringing)

20:09.600 --> 20:11.801
Well, as you can see,
we have followed

20:11.869 --> 20:14.137
Your exact specifications.

20:14.205 --> 20:16.072
Wait, where's my puppy?

20:16.140 --> 20:17.674
She specifically
asked for a puppy.

20:17.742 --> 20:19.509
Mercedes:
This is unbelievable.

20:19.577 --> 20:22.178
How am I supposed
to work like this?
Don't worry. Puckerman is

20:22.246 --> 20:25.415
Out right now scouring pounds
for the perfect pomeranian.

20:25.483 --> 20:27.417
Good. This is almost
worthy of the artist

20:27.485 --> 20:29.486
Doing the closing
number at the benefit.

20:29.553 --> 20:32.021
Well, actually, um, sunshine

20:32.089 --> 20:34.357
Is going to be doing
the last number, because

20:34.425 --> 20:36.126
She's bringing in hundreds
of people.

20:36.193 --> 20:38.061
And so, I'll go on

20:38.129 --> 20:39.796
Before sunshine
because, I'm, well, me,

20:39.864 --> 20:43.166
And, uh, Ms. Holliday and
mercedes will go on before me.

20:43.234 --> 20:44.634
Fine.

20:45.970 --> 20:47.871
But Ms. Jones isn't
happy about it.

20:47.938 --> 20:49.205
In exchange, she's demanding

20:49.273 --> 20:51.341
That during the day
of the benefit, her feet

20:51.409 --> 20:53.476
Never touch
the ground.
Excuse me?

20:53.544 --> 20:55.412
Oh, did you not see
celine's wedding?
Carried in.

20:55.479 --> 20:56.679
Cher's comeback tour?
Carried in.

20:56.747 --> 20:57.847
Gaga at the grammys?

20:57.915 --> 20:59.749
Carried the hell in.

20:59.817 --> 21:01.418
Um, I'm sorry. Are-are

21:01.485 --> 21:04.754
