carried in in a giant egg?

21:07.758 --> 21:09.726
We'll get back to you.

21:12.288 --> 21:13.689
And that was
the spanish classroom.

21:13.757 --> 21:15.624
And of course,
you know the choir room.

21:15.692 --> 21:17.059
Brittany:
Hey, you guys, you better

21:17.127 --> 21:18.661
Get in the auditorium.
The show's about to start.

21:18.728 --> 21:19.995
It's going to be a
full house, ya'll.

21:20.063 --> 21:21.797
Got to get there early
to get a good seat.

21:21.865 --> 21:23.699
We'll be there in a minute.
I'm just showing blaine around.

21:23.767 --> 21:25.234
Thanks for coming and
supporting us, guys.

21:25.301 --> 21:26.368
It's really cool.

21:26.436 --> 21:27.569
Bye.

21:30.106 --> 21:31.707
Oh, you miss them.

21:31.775 --> 21:34.743
What the hell
are you two doing here?

21:34.811 --> 21:36.245
We're here for the benefit.
Don't tell me you're going.

21:36.312 --> 21:37.579
I wouldn't be caught dead.

21:37.647 --> 21:39.448
I was pumping iron
in the gym,

21:39.516 --> 21:41.083
And one of the guys told me
you two were here

21:41.151 --> 21:42.785
Spreading your fairy dust
all over the place.

21:42.852 --> 21:44.286
Would you just give it up?

21:44.354 --> 21:46.121
You can live whatever lie
you want, but don't pretend

21:46.189 --> 21:47.723
The three of us don't know
what's really going on here.

21:47.791 --> 21:49.525
You don't know squat, butt boy.

21:49.592 --> 21:52.461
Hey, no, guys, stop!
Real brave with your fists,

21:52.529 --> 21:54.496
But you're a coward when
it comes to the truth.

21:54.564 --> 21:57.366
