douchebag another day.

22:17.353 --> 22:20.556
Oh, and also, I have
razorblades hidden in my hair.

22:20.623 --> 22:21.890
Mm-hmm. Tons.

22:21.958 --> 22:23.692
Just all up in there.

22:23.760 --> 22:25.894
Mm-hmm.

22:25.962 --> 22:26.995
